text:
The North Georgia State Fair has been canceled for the first time since World War II. It was scheduled to begin next month.

Organizers are planning to hold a “Taste of the Fair” drive-thru experience, giving people a chance to taste favorite fair foods. https://t.co/8vOQcpedqh
